---
title: Shrimp, White Bean & Kale Caesar Salad with Broccoli, Garlicky Panko & Toasted Ciabatta Points
description: Our chefs' riff on a vegan Caesar salad is sure to check all the boxes. You’ll pair a base of kale, white beans, and roasted broccoli with a creamy dressing featuring vegan Worcestershire sauce, lemon, mustard, and nutritional yeast—a flavor powerhouse that helps simulate the nutty, cheesy flavor of Parm, minus the dairy. A shower of crispy garlic panko and ciabatta toast points complete the meal.
